        "created_at": "2022-11-17T17:40:54.422Z",
        "cooked": "<p>With Rayas out of reach, looking to try one of these off a restaurant list. I believe they are all pretty closely priced, and are the CdR, and not Syrah. I\u2019ve never had one before, so looking for red fruited pretties\u2026with a hint of that Rayas magic? Thanks!</p>\n<p>1999<br>\n2001<br>\n2007<br>\n2008</p>",
