        "username": "Kris_Patten",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/kris_patten/{size}/2869_2.png",
        "created_at": "2022-11-17T19:08:31.997Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t know why but I was thinking the question as what Pialade.  Shouldn\u2019t post while working on a project.  Guess I always say Rayas, Pignan, Fonsalette Rouge, Blanc or Syrah and CdR I associate with Pialade from having sold them.</p>\n<p>If Fonsalette Rouge, I\u2019d only flip 2001 and 2007 followed by 1999 and 2008.</p>\n<p>Thanks for keeping me honest.</p>",
