        "created_at": "2022-11-17T20:48:37.341Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Had the 2007 two years ago. Was already drinking pretty well back then for my taste. Can only imagine it is even better now. Loved 2008 Rayas, but not sure if 2008 Fonsalette has turned out as good.</p>\n<p>Also important to note that i often prefer wines on the younger side.</p>",
